&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;As a Controls Applications Engineer, you will be the controls subject matter expert supporting the design and delivery of material handling systems for parcel&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;distribution&amp;nbsp;and fulfillment environments. You will work closely with both precontract and post contract teams to translate client&amp;nbsp;needs and&amp;nbsp;requirements into well-defined&amp;nbsp;controls&amp;nbsp;solutions. In this role, you will collaborate with internal engineering teams, estimators, and external controls and electrical suppliers to develop designs, scopes of work, and estimates that support successful project execution. You will move between multiple projects at&amp;nbsp;different stages, helping shape solutions early in the sales cycle and ensuring controls requirements are clearly defined and executed as projects move forward.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;What&amp;nbsp;You’ll&amp;nbsp;Be Doing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Develop&amp;nbsp;field placement drawings&amp;nbsp;based on system requirements and project specifications.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Estimate field wiring and&amp;nbsp;controls&amp;nbsp;components.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Review client RFPs to understand controls and electrical requirements.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Develop RFPs for subcontractors and help define clear scopes of work.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Partner with&amp;nbsp;various internal&amp;nbsp;teams&amp;nbsp;to su

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;About the Role: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot; data-start=&quot;109&quot; data-end=&quot;610&quot;&gt;At DCS, we don&#39;t just design automation systems—we bring them to life. As a Controls Commissioning Engineer, you&#39;ll play a critical role in transforming engineered solutions into fully operational systems at customer sites. You&#39;ll partner with Controls Engineers, Project Managers, Site Managers, Mechanical Engineers, Software teams, customers, and field technicians to commission complex material handling and warehouse automation systems that power some of the world&#39;s most recognizable brands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;615&quot; data-end=&quot;907&quot;&gt;This is an ideal opportunity for someone who enjoys hands-on problem solving, thrives in fast-paced project environments, and wants to see their work come to life in the field. Every project presents new challenges, technologies, and opportunities to build expertise in industrial automation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;912&quot; data-end=&quot;1371&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;912&quot; data-end=&quot;1166&quot;&gt;This role is remote-based, allowing you to establish your home office anywhere within the continental United States. From there, you&#39;ll travel up to 75% to customer sites throughout the commissioning, startup, testing, and go-live phases of projects.&lt;/strong&gt; If you enjoy variety, working directly with customers, and seeing the impact of your work firsthand, this role offers the opportunity to support cutting-edge automation installations across North America.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Execute&amp;nbsp;on&lt;/span&gt;‑&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;site&amp;nbsp;commissioning of automated material handling systems, including conveyors, sorters,&amp;nbsp;merges, and supporting subsystems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Perform I/O checkout,&amp;nbsp;safety checks,&amp;nbsp;device validation, and field wiring verification to ensure system readiness.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Configure, test, and troubleshoot&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;PLC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;HMI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;VFD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;, and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;industrial network&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;components (e.g., Ethernet/IP,&amp;nbsp;OPCUA, MQTT, IO-Link).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Validate system functionality against design specifications and functional requirements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Collaborate with mechanical, electrical, software, and project engineering teams to resolve issues and&amp;nbsp;optimize&amp;nbsp;system

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;About the Role: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Controls Engineer, you will lead the hardware aspects of controls projects throughout the design phase; from concept and component selection to electrical system design. You will play a key role in delivering reliable, scalable, and innovative automation systems for high-profile material handling customers. Additionally, you will contribute to the evolution of DCS’s electrical standards, product offerings, and team capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Sound like you? Read on.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;In this role, you will:  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead controls electrical designs and assists with implementation for material handling systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design electrical systems, including field device placement, control panel layouts, and electrical schematics using AutoCAD Electrical or EPLAN.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Select components, design networks, develop Bills of Materials (BOMs), and validate equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Program PLCs and oversee system commissioning, debugging, and validation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide on-site troubleshooting and technical support during installation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure projects are delivered on time, within scope, and to customer satisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain controls and electrical design and installation standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with vendors to evaluate and implement emerging Material Handling System technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify cost-saving opportunities through value engineering without compromising performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor engineers and contribute to knowledge-sharing across the Controls team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in Controls team initiatives, process development, and tool creation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support recruiting efforts and provide feedback on technology/software vendors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain open, timely communication with project teams and leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent DCS with professionalism during site visits, customer meetings, and supplier interactions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to a positive, team-oriented culture that emphasizes growth and accountability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend weekly controls meetings and internal training sessions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We’re Excited About You Because:  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;You have 1+ years of relevant experience (or 3+ years without

