&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Drive accountability across all project stakeholders and functional teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
