&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Participate in customer-specific safety programs, including STAR, Amazon BOLT, Avetta, and other site-specific initiatives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;qu

