&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;95&quot; data-end=&quot;112&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;114&quot; data-end=&quot;509&quot;&gt;As a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;119&quot; data-end=&quot;147&quot;&gt;Senior Controls Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll lead end-to-end controls delivery for complex material handling systems, from early concept and component selection through programming, commissioning, and customer handoff. You’ll be a key contributor on high-profile projects, trusted to design reliable, scalable automation solutions and solve problems in real time, both on the floor and in the field.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;511&quot; data-end=&quot;794&quot;&gt;Beyond project execution, you’ll help shape the future of DCS’s controls capabilities by influencing standards, reusable tools, and how the team works together. If you enjoy owning technical outcomes, mentoring others, and pushing controls design forward, this role is built for you.&lt;/p&gt;
