&lt;li data-start=&quot;899&quot; data-end=&quot;1042&quot;&gt;Develop electrical designs including field device layouts, control panel designs, and electrical schematics using AutoCAD Electrical or EPLAN&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1045&quot; data-end=&quot;1138&quot;&gt;Select components, design control networks, develop BOMs, and validate equipment selections&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1141&quot; data-end=&quot;1187&quot;&gt;Program PLCs and develop HMI/SCADA solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1190&quot; data-end=&quot;1281&quot;&gt;Commission and debug systems on-site; support testing, startup, and validation activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1284&quot; data-end=&quot;1375&quot;&gt;Provide technical support during installation and perform field troubleshooting as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1378&quot; data-end=&quot;1448&quot;&gt;Deliver projects on time, within scope, and to customer expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1451&quot; data-end=&quot;1560&quot;&gt;Contribute to the development and maintenance of controls standards, templates, and reusable code libraries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1563&quot; data-end=&quot;1649&quot;&gt;Lead or support R&amp;amp;D efforts and internal initiatives to expand controls capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1652&quot; data-end=&quot;1717&quot;&gt;Partner with vendors to evaluate and implement new technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1720&quot; data-end=&quot;1802&quot;&gt;Identify value-engineering opportunities without compromising system performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1805&quot; data-end=&quot;1926&quot;&gt;Serve as a senior technical contributor on cross-functional project teams (Project Management, Mechanical, Field, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1929&quot; data-end=&quot;2008&quot;&gt;Mentor junior engineers and actively share knowledge across the Controls team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2011&quot; data-end=&quot;2097&quot;&gt;Participate in controls team initiatives, process improvements, and tool development&lt;/li&gt;
