&lt;p&gt;As a&amp;nbsp;Site Manager&amp;nbsp;at DCS, you will&amp;nbsp;be our on-location&amp;nbsp;point-person,&amp;nbsp;managing&amp;nbsp;our project&amp;nbsp;execution.&amp;nbsp;You will collaborate with your&amp;nbsp;project team, raise awareness of on-site challenges and be a part of the resolution. We will count on you to&amp;nbsp;oversee&amp;nbsp;our contractors and&amp;nbsp;vendors, partners, installers, risk management, and above all keeping&amp;nbsp;everybody safe.&amp;nbsp;We will appreciate your&amp;nbsp;on-site leadership, your communication on daily reports,&amp;nbsp;your impressive teamwork skills,&amp;nbsp;ability to manage project milestones, all the while upholding our Five DCS core values; Be Bold, Be Reliable, Be a Problem Solver, Be Learning Oriented, and Be Easy to Work With.&lt;/p&gt;
