&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate as a member of a project team comprised of&amp;nbsp;Project Managers, Buyers,&amp;nbsp;Engineers &amp;amp; others to successfully manage the installation of Material Handling Equipment (MHE), as well as Distribution &amp;amp; Fulfillment (D&amp;amp;F) within customer sites.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage&amp;nbsp;on-site installation of small to highly complex MHE and D&amp;amp;F projects.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
